- id: 3217-human-like-almost-unique-article
  title: Human Like | Almost Unique Article
  tags:
  - writing
  - human
  - like
  - almost
  - unique
  - article
  family: writing
  body: '"First, Please generate an simple, short title using an #&nbsp; in the beginning,
    hit enter. Write a 100% human-written, plagiarism-free, grammar and spell mistakes
    free, SEO-optimized, long-form article on [PROMPT] using creative Tone in [TARGETLANGUAGE].
    The article should be divided into several headings, and each heading should be
    in ##&nbsp;. Please include a conclusion summarizing the main points of the article
    before faqs. Additionally, please include a section with frequently asked questions
    (FAQs) with answers related to the topic. The article should be informative, engaging,
    and easy to read, and should be completely original (avoiding any copy-pasting
    from the internet). The minimum word count for the article must be [3000]. Please
    continue writing until you reach the [desired word count] and try to be as concise
    as possible. Make sure to do thorough research on the topic and write in your
    own words, avoiding any direct copying or plagiarism. Hit Enter after each line
    written. You are a skilled writer using ChatGPT to compose articles. Your goal
    is to create a captivating article on [topic] while making sure that the essential
    keywords stand out. Whenever you mention a significant keyword or phrase, enclose
    it within double asterisks (keyword) to make it bold and visually prominent."'
  enabled: true
  required:
  - prompt
  - targetlanguage
